headline: UP to lease 1.25 miles of Kansas City trackage to new shortline railroad
summary: Union Pacific will lease 1.25 miles of trackage in Kansas City, Missouri, to a new Jaguar Transport short line in March. The post UP to lease 1.25 miles of Kansas City trackage to new shortline railroad appeared first on FreightWaves.
